init_text:
Is Listening to a Book Just as Good as Reading It?

Do you listen to audiobooks? What are the benefits, in your opinion, of listening instead of reading? Are there advantages to reading that cannot be gained by listening? Which method do you prefer? Why?

---

In my opinion,

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Also, reading a book is somewhat like immersing oneself in the world of the author.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I believe you need to put your full attention into it.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: We should support them for that reason.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Many of the rare and out of print books have been converted to audio format.
